reviews.review_text:
Very Nice Overall sound is very good although there are a few speed issues where it sounds like the band is slowing slightly. This recording sounds as if the original tape was damaged due to heat or moisture. It is really pretty minimal.

However to make up for any technical difficulties, the band turned in an excellent performance that night.
